title: GAME OF THRONES Season 8 Episode 4 New Photos, Clues, and Predictions!
author: Think Story
comment: Just quick video today guys with some info on the new photos released by HBO! You can check'em out here: https://ew.com/tv/2019/05/01/game-thrones-season-8-episode-4/
I'm just thankful Amazon have Invested heavily into making a lord of the rings TV show to keep this genre going in the future
The ending is easy to figure out. Remember when Ned wrote “rightful heir” instead of Joffrey’s name? Arya will kill Cersei and Gendry will take the throne as Robert’s last known son.
The next episode will be AMAZING! Then we'll get another AWESOME breakdown by you! Well shucks...are we spoiled or what?! ☺
0:44 Anyone else notice the tower on the right has several barrels. Is this what Cersei is gazing at? Could this be wildfire?
description:
In this video we look at the new photos released today from HBO for Game of Thrones Season 8 Episode 4 "The Last War" and breakdown some of the clues they hold. Predictions and theories abound!
